entry.title: Winter Storm Warning issued November 15 at 12:39PM AKST until November 16 at 3:00AM AKST by NWS
entry.summary: ...SNOW FOR THE KLONDIKE HIGHWAY... .An approaching warm front will cross into the panhandle this evening bringing more moisture to the area. This precipitation is expected to fall as snow, especially across the the Klondike Highway. Snow is expected to be the heaviest during the overnight hours before rates diminish during the morning hours on Thursday.
